Package com.brestats.model.data

Class Gare

java.lang.Object
com.brestats.model.data.Gare
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class Gare extends Object implements Model
The Gare class represents a train station with specific attributes such as its code, name, type (freight or passenger), and associated municipality. It implements the Model interface and provides methods to access and manipulate its data.

This class includes methods to get and set the station's code, name, type (freight or passenger), and associated municipality, as well as to return a string representation of the station.
